<paragraph blockId="13.[183,1397,290,1861]" pageId="13" pageNumber="704">D. 1. finschi Matschie, 1916 — North Coastal Ranges of New Guinea W of Wewak; also Yapen I, in Cenderawasih (= Geelvink) Bay.</paragraph>
